        <updateDate>2007-05-01T20:14:38Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Recognizing Addiction as a Disease Act of 2007 - Amends the Public Health Service Act and related enactments to redesignate: (1) the National Institute on Drug Abuse as the National Institute on Diseases of Addiction; and (2) the National Institute on Alcohol Abuse and Alcoholism as the National Institute on Alcohol Disorders and Health.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
